title: Tangerine Dream - Berlin Vernissage - 2016-01-30
description:
Not just Tangerine Dream, but the whole set. Check my account for more.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)


Tangerine Dream - Picture Palace Music - Ulrich Schnauss - Hoshiko Yamane
Berlin Vernissage Edgar Froese & Bianca Froese-Acquaye 2016-01-30, Berliner Festspiele Foyer

A vernissage for the zoom-o-graphics & acrylic paintings by Edgar Froese (1944-2015) and Bianca Froese-Acquaye (The Art of How to Dream) with performances of Tangerine Dream and members.

Tracklist:

01 - Hoshiko Yamane set
02 - Ulrich Schnauss set
03 - Picture Palace Music set
04 - Tangerine Dream set

Enjoy these nice concerts, some noise from audience in this club like event. Also the volume of the concerts was at the low side.
In the beginning of the Picture Palace Music set you can hear that Ulrich Schnauss computer is not turned off...
This is the first ever concert with Tangerine Dream without Edgar Froese! Sic!
